from bitcode and fix llvm-gcc to do everything up to bitcode generation.

Some issues that should be remedied as part of this:
* make it possible to run the &amp;quot;compiler driver&amp;quot; without having to specify
   include and link paths
* have predfined symbols for pnacl and have no misleading predefined symbols
 such as __linux__, __x86__, etc 
